org.apache.zeppelin.cluster

Class ClusterManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.zeppelin.cluster.ClusterManager
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ClusterManagerClient, ClusterManagerServer

    public abstract class ClusterManager
extends Object
    The base class for cluster management, including the following implementations 1. RaftClient as the raft client 2. Threading to provide retry after cluster metadata submission failure 3. Cluster monitoring
